{"id":271094,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-长沙李香等维权人士家属在火车站派出所/","date":"2012-12-28T10:15:58Z","modified":"2012-12-28T10:15:58Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙李香等维权人士家属在火车站派出所报案遭推诿（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员李军报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月，长沙维权人士刘华、李颂明、曾武、邓生记四人集体遭到拘押，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>，这四名维权人士的亲属和朋友准备赴京，在火车站被强行非法绑架。</span>  </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，维权人士家属李香等来长沙车站派出所就遭到绑架报案，等了三个小时了，警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">093571</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">093816</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">093723</span><span>的警察没有给家属做笔录，还把参与绑架的人都通知来了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>等了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>个多小时后，警察终于答应给家属立案侦查了，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 094028</span><span>警官为李香做笔录，做了报案询问笔录，做完后李香要他复印一份给自己，他不肯，字都没有让李香签就走了，按法律程序做笔录应该有两人以上才合法。李香问他要立案告知书，他说没有，李香又问他是否会立案，他说不知道，李香又问他要不予立案告知书，他说没有。家属在派出所里坚持要立案告知书，或不立案告知书，等待了数小时后，当班的刘健所长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">094505</span><span>让大家明天早上再到派出所来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，家属在车站派出所从早上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点等到下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点还没有等到立案告知书，刘健所长约家属来，却自己躲着不见，打发一个没有穿工作服，没名没姓的人来忽悠家属，要家属回家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>下午三点多钟，警号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">094967</span><span>的警察又重新给李香做了笔录，报案回执、立案告知书或不立案告知书，已然没有见到。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家一直在等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">094505</span><span>刘健所长到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>点多都下班了，还是无人理睬。几位老奶奶冻得实在受不了了，就找到二楼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">094616</span><span>胥所长办公室里要答复，还有缪警官也在，刚开始要一个个讲，家属都做了笔录，要报案回执，立案或不立案告知书，却都没有明确答复</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/12/blog-post_400.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/12/blog-post_400.html</a></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-v7q17Eo3Nho/UN1GPf_FMAI/AAAAAAAAXtY/dSeAlPYrMMU/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"237\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-v7q17Eo3Nho/UN1GPf_FMAI/AAAAAAAAXtY/dSeAlPYrMMU/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3A3-1Sony30/UN1GSuKsORI/AAAAAAAAXtg/vxWaeWugGrM/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3A3-1Sony30/UN1GSuKsORI/AAAAAAAAXtg/vxWaeWugGrM/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"239\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}